game.name: Dora Taco
game.description:
Dora is a very cute and intelligent girl with a lot of hobbies. She also loves spending some quality time in the kitchen trying out new delicious recipes for herself. Although this beautiful girl is crazy for all types of food items, tacos are her favourite ones. For this reason, she is planning to try her hands in making this recipe. Hope you would help her to prepare tasty tacos and give her a chance to enjoy the best lunch she has ever taken.  

Dora used to have this recipe without going to the nearest restaurant. She only enjoys the taste of her loving and most favorite snack if she prepares it on her own. So, she has planned out today to make tacos at home to have the fun at her own time. The key of achieving the goal of this brand new cooking game is to follow the instructions. Make sure that you also stick to the recipe in order to make these crunchy tacos. 

She trusts on your chef skills, so please do not let her feel low. She will definitely feel proud on you if the final results are really awesome. It is in your hands to allow this cute girl enjoy this traditional meal in the comfort of her own home. The quicker you complete your job; the higher score you will be able to see on the scoreboard in the end of this free online cooking game: Dora Taco.
